			<li class="alt" id="comment-92023">

			<div class="user_avatar"><a href="http://olegmokhov.com" title="Oleg Mokhov" rel="nofollow"><img alt='' src='http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/2c6311a2df6d809dfde65c473991d938?s=40&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.doshdosh.com%2Fcomment-avatar.jpg%3Fs%3D40&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' /></a></div>				<div class="entry"> 
