			<li class="" id="comment-92142">

			<div class="user_avatar"><a href="http://twitter.com/arthurbarbato" title="Arthur Barbato" rel="nofollow"><img alt='' src='http://www.gravatar.com/avatar/0245e02533bf248cce4c31fdc7957efc?s=40&amp;d=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.doshdosh.com%2Fcomment-avatar.jpg%3Fs%3D40&amp;r=PG' class='avatar avatar-40 photo' height='40' width='40' /></a></div>				<div class="entry"> 
